138.2	Alvin_Toffler	Alvin Toffler	Alvin Toffler (born October 4, 1928 in New York City) is an American writer and futurist, known for his works discussing the digital revolution, communication revolution, corporate revolution and technological singularity.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e1/Alvin_Toffler_02.jpg/210px-Alvin_Toffler_02.jpg
